      <title>Digi 将以 7.5 亿欧元的价格向麦格理主导的集团出售光纤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/digi-to-sell-fiber-to-macquarie-led-group-for-750-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Digi Communications NV 已同意将其在西班牙的部分光纤网络出售给麦格理集团有限公司领导的财团，因为该公司正在寻求资金来支付其在该国的扩张计划，包括从 Orange-Masmovil 交易中购买补救措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/digi-to-sell-fiber-to-macquarie-led-group-for-750-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 10:24:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
